criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Pacients admitted in ICU that are more than 18 years;

          -  MV for more than 24 hours;

          -  Assignature of the free and informed consent form by a family member or responsable
             adult.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Death before SBT;

          -  Tracheostomy;

          -  Self-extubation;

          -  Accidental extubation;

          -  Absence of signature of informed consent.
